Subject: [PATCH 114/170] drm/vc4: Add an interface for capturing the GPU state
 after a hang.

This can be parsed with vc4-gpu-tools tools for trying to figure out
what was going on.

Signed-off-by: Eric Anholt <eric@anholt.net>
